info.name: Flower Witch Mary Bell
info.description:
Mary Bell, a magical girl who looks like a girl around five years old, comes to the human world from a magical world called "Flower Magic World", and helps and encourages people.

(Source: Wikipedia)

moreInfo.japanese: 花の魔法使いマリーベル
moreInfo.synonyms: Floral Magician Mary Bell, Hana no Mahou Tsukai Maribell, Floral Elf Mary Bell, Flower Witch Marybell
